<div class="content wrapper cf">
  <div class="upload-file">
    <h2 class="albert-light-normal">Upload File</h2>
    <p>Bulk upload of articles with a file that contains any combination of
       DOIs and PMIDs for PLOS articles, one per line.  The application will retrieve
       the top entries until the maximum of 500 is reached.  <a href="/sample_upload_file.csv">Sample File</a></p>
    <%= form_tag("/upload", :method => "post", :class => "upload-file-form", :multipart => true) do %>
      <%= label_tag(:"upload-file-field", "File path", :class => "hidden") %>
      <%= file_field_tag(:"upload-file-field") %>
      <%= submit_tag("Upload File", :class => "button-hover-dark-black submit-btn upload-file-btn") %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
